query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (k.keyword like '%quest%') AND cct1.kind in ('crew','cast','complete+verified') AND t.production_year < 1991 AND (t.title like '%battle%' OR t.title like '%spaceship%' OR t.title like '%treasure%' OR t.title like '%game%' OR t.title like '%chair%') AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','cast') AND mi_idx.info > '4.0' AND n.gender in ('m') AND it2.info in ('books','death notes','tech info','LD status of availablility','death date','book','LD review') AND it1.info in ('admissions','interviews','death notes','LD audio noise','LD quality program','LD disc format','mpaa','LD digital sound','LD picture format','LD additional information') AND mi.info in ('German','Hebrew','Rotuman','Inuktitut','Vietnamese','English','Macedonian','Serbian','Serbo-Croatian','Irish Gaelic','Greek','Persian')
